347
00:22:02,071 --> 00:22:04,865
<i>Because I have a strong desire</i>

348
00:22:04,949 --> 00:22:09,453
<i>To accomplish</i>

349
00:22:14,750 --> 00:22:19,296
<i>I'm not weak enough to believe</i>

350
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:25,386
<i>Any of these negative perceptions</i>

351
00:22:25,886 --> 00:22:31,225
<i>I'm a trickster
who doesn't know solitude</i>

352
00:22:35,479 --> 00:22:37,147
PREVIEW

353
00:22:37,606 --> 00:22:42,361
Yeah... I know I probably look
pretty bad in here...

354
00:22:43,028 --> 00:22:45,447
